52
Scheduling. gOntt Plug-in
D5.3.2
 gOntt helps in scheduling an ontology network development.
 gOntt
is a NeOn
plug-in for integrating the NeOn
Methodology and the NeOn Toolkit. 
– gOntt
provides
filling cards, workflows, and methodological
guidelines. 
– gOntt triggers the NeOn plug-ins associated to each process and 
activity planned.
